70396042.title: An Extra Special Episode
70396042.extract: "An Extra Special Episode" is the eleventh episode of the fourteenth season of the American television series RuPaul's Drag Race. It originally aired on March 18, 2022. The episode has seven contestants compete in a series of lip-sync contests to determine who would be eliminated from the competition. Jasmine Kennedie is eliminated after losing a final match against Bosco.
